- What does that mean?</i>

591
00:42:10,100 --> 00:42:11,980
I can be the consort prince, too?

592
00:42:11,980 --> 00:42:13,139
What do you mean?

593
00:42:13,140 --> 00:42:16,459
Young Khan, you said that the marriage will be a token of friendship.

594
00:42:16,460 --> 00:42:19,960
Everybody here wants to develop a friendship with Great Tang.

595
00:42:19,960 --> 00:42:22,859
Such being the case, the able man shall win.

596
00:42:22,859 --> 00:42:25,538
Your Majesty of Great Tang, how about holding a contest?

597
00:42:25,539 --> 00:42:28,579
It will be fair to all of us.

598
00:42:31,679 --> 00:42:33,079
Good idea.

599
00:42:33,779 --> 00:42:36,939
Only the winner shall have Noble Princess Yongan.

600
00:42:36,940 --> 00:42:39,840
Young Khan, do you dare to accept the challenge?

601
00:42:44,639 --> 00:42:47,019
Well, Young Khan, are you scared?

602
00:42:47,019 --> 00:42:50,079
That's nonsense. Why should I be scared?

603
00:42:50,600 --> 00:42:55,078
Good. Young Khan is truly a hero.

604
00:42:55,078 --> 00:42:56,680
Such being the case,

605
00:42:56,680 --> 00:42:59,678
